    <string name="helptext">
        - Starting a game:\nTo start a new game, select an objective from the list of objectives
        with your desired location, number of points and difficulty and hit the Select button.
        \n
        \nThe difficulty of each objective can be viewed on the map depending on the size of the circle
        surrounding it. The higher the difficulty, the closer to the objective you have to be.
        \n\n\n
        - Logging out:\nHad enough of EindhovenGo for now? Open up the main menu, pull out the drawer
        and under the Other options you will find the Logout button.
        \n\n\n
